    <description>Automation to populate Demo Path on Lead or Contact after the creation of a CP Event

8/13/24 - Updated logic to only run off of events created by CP Queue User or Integration User as Sales Users were causing unintended updates to Demo Path</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>formDemoPath</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(CONTAINS({!$Record.Queue_Name_CP__c},&apos;Call Me Now&apos;),&apos;Call Me Now&apos;,
    IF(CONTAINS({!$Record.Queue_Name_CP__c},&apos;Schedule&apos;),&apos;Schedule&apos;,&apos;Chase Me: Chili Piper&apos;))</expression>
    </formulas>
